# yielde-skills/_pending/

Holds bulk-imported Hermes skill drafts awaiting Chris's `--operator chris`
promotion (Phase 7 deliverable 6d).

Drafts land here via:

    node scripts/import-hermes.mjs --bulk [--filter S] [--limit N]

Promotion stays Chris-only via the explicit curator gate:

    node scripts/import-hermes.mjs --promote <name> --operator chris

The yielde-bridge `/inspect/hermes-pending` panel surfaces what's here
read-only — Bridge cannot promote anything itself.

This .gitkeep stays so the dir tracks empty between bulk runs.
